4 c. Include the following value columns:
5 (1) Total number of vaccines administered for the indexed cohort; and
6 (2) Total number of deaths for the indexed cohort occurring within one, three,
7 seven, fourteen, twenty-one, and thirty days of the exact vaccination date
8 and continuing with columns reporting the total number of deaths for
9 additional thirty-day intervals through seven hundred twenty days since
10 vaccination, with the total deaths counted for each interval being cumulative
11 up to that period.
12 d. A redaction may not be made for a low count unless the department of health and
13 human services is expressly notified of a privacy issue regarding the count.
